持有攻擊性武器（laser pointer ) 100%入罪就扮盲唔答。 <br />\n全世界都知上訴庭 = 加刑庭  <br />\n一提就死撐證據薄弱好難上訴成功<br />\n<br />\n「銅鑼灣831中場總結]」 共16人被控暴動，全部裁決均已出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2439185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2439185</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>[/quote]"},{"pid":"896433fa74fb0f8438d9204d821a3fc447656330","tid":2459251,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"0ef092530702eb492a0b3396cfb98f2cd32f4b99","tid":2459251,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9e67adb661110f8ac67613b513ba3cf5502812","tid":2459251,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e73d146d43aea22e29d48575f43efeb147845e0d","tid":2459251,"uid":127575,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"連登左膠登粉唔該請回應下兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120214%2Fphoto%2F0214-00176-059b1.jpg&amp;h=1e6a35e3&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"佢地繼續圍爐<br />\n繼續大愛共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncctoy會員撐侵偉論收集區(2)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378750</a>"},{"pid":"91928f3cfe21e2b03e3c5488ead1639f381824a8","tid":2459251,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"5002b0b0f6f479de9c1906c23e7918166a8759aa","tid":2459251,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/